          <h2>9. Termination</h2>
          <p>You may terminate your account at any time by cancelling your subscription. We may terminate your access to the Service for violation of these Terms.</p>
          <p>Upon termination, your right to use the Service will cease immediately, and any data stored in your account may be deleted.</p>
